		"description": "{html}<div><p>Is it possible to build in runnable threads? Too many times I've\nbeen running intensive XHR requests, and they lock up the UI\nportion of the app. Would it be possible to implement such a\nfeature to allow the request to run in the background, whilst still\nkeeping the UI free?</p>\n<p>I've thrown around some code today that isn't of any quality,\nbut with the Ti proxies and such, I don't think it would be hard to\nimplement a ThreadManager module (for namesake).</p>\n<p>Andrew</p></div>{html}",
